<title>CHINA: Iwai's posts year net loss vs profit.</title>
<headline>Iwai's posts year net loss vs profit.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-07-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended March 31</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	    22.8 loss  vs 14.9 profit</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)     nil	  vs 5.0</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	   7.09 debit vs nil</p>
<p>    Net			     28.61 loss vs 16.13 profit</p>
<p>    Turnover			120.97     vs 120.82</p>
<p>    Company name		  Iwai's International Holdings Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		   Sept 23-26</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	    N/A</p>
<p>NOTE - The company is an apparel retailer. Exceptional loss is mainly from fixed assets written off in closing down of shops.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6370</p>
